# Allowlist pattern: exclude everything, then include what we need
*

# Workspace Cargo files
!Cargo.toml
!Cargo.lock

# Rust crates
!shatter-core/
!shatter-cli/
!shatter-rust/

# Language frontends (needed by build.rs)
!shatter-ts/
!shatter-go/

# Exclude nested build artifacts even within included dirs
shatter-ts/node_modules/
shatter-ts/dist/
shatter-rust/target/
